data.description: Welcome to your dream rustic cottage in the heart of Upper Lafayette, where charm meets comfort! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a true gem, boasting a unique metal roof, open-concept living, and a location that's just minutes, Volley Beach, and the new Parc de Oaks food truck park. As you approach the property, you'll be captivated by the inviting front porch, perfect for sipping your morning coffee or enjoying the sunset with friends and family. Stepping inside, you'll immediately notice the warm and welcoming atmosphere, featuring rustic finishes and a spacious open concept design that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The Charming kitchen has tons of counter space and a center island that serves as a gathering spot for meal preparation and casual dining. This cottage offers three comfortable bedrooms, each providing a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with a inviting Jacuzzi tub, offering the perfect spot for relaxation and rejuvenation.   The charm of this property extends beyond the interior, as the generous lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or even expansion. The metal roof not only adds to the cottage's rustic aesthetic but also promises durability and longevity, the vinyl siding and soffits make this home so easy to maintain!   Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful property yours! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm and convenience of this cottage for yourself.
